      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/lysfangha/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team project:&lt;/strong&gt; See &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mobygames.com/game/217756/lysfanga-the-time-shift-warrior/credits/windows&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xD;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xD;&#xA;&gt;credits&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;svg id=&#34;external-link&#34; class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tech stack:&lt;/strong&gt; Unity 2021, C#, Visual Studio, Perforce, Jira&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platforms:&lt;/strong&gt; Windows (&lt;a href=&#34;https://store.steampowered.com/app/2161620&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xD;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xD;&#xA;&gt;Steam&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;svg id=&#34;external-link&#34; class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://store.epicgames.com/p/lysfanga-9608f2&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xD;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xD;&#xA;&gt;Epic Store&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;svg id=&#34;external-link&#34; class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;) / &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/lysfanga-the-time-shift-warrior-switch&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xD;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xD;&#xA;&gt;Nintendo Switch&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;svg id=&#34;external-link&#34; class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Rewind time to create clones of your past-selves, and fight with an army of your own. Become legion and triumph over hordes of monsters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
