      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/turbo-engine/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;image-figure not-prose my-8&#34; &#xD;&#xA;        data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;true&#34;&#xD;&#xA;        data-gallery-type=&#34;auto&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;image-container&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;img&#xD;&#xA;    src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/TurboEngine/TurboEngineStamp.png&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    alt=&#34;TurboEngine logo&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    data-gallery-src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/TurboEngine/TurboEngineStamp.png&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    data-gallery-alt=&#34;TurboEngine logo&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    data-gallery-title=&#34;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team project:&lt;/strong&gt; 4 programmers&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dev time:&lt;/strong&gt; 5 months (school)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tech stack:&lt;/strong&gt; C++17, Visual Studio 2017, Git, Trello, Python 3.7, Qt, GLFW, PhysX, FMOD, nlohmann json, OpenGL, Freetype, stb_image, Glew, Autodesk FBX SDK, TinyObjLoader, SOL2, RuntimeCompiledCPlusPlus&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platforms:&lt;/strong&gt; Windows&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The Turbo Engine is a 3D game engine 3 amazing teammates and I developed as third year students. We also developed an editor, and made a small game with it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
